item.title: Dr. Yasir delivering his talk on Demistify AI
item.description:
Congratulations to Dr. Yasir for delivering his talk on Demistify AI.

Our InSyAp member Dr. Yasir said in his linkend post that he enjoyed discussing AI, sustainability, and ethics, supporting my colleague Alejandro Jiménez Rodríguez at the event hosted by Innovation Network South Yorkshire, Sheffield Digital, the University of Sheffield, and Sheffield Hallam University. It was a great opportunity to connect with regional businesses and to catch up with familiar faces. https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7324098488118484993/
